{"tid":1498282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！東華三院主任憤怒了","createTime":"2019-08-23T10:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T19:11:58.000Z","uid":202269,"like":852,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"e22728f28c3cff1bf844aeb566ed60b96bd3e654","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"今日一班東華中學生去咗上環總部交聯署信<br />\n東華都好比面派咗中學部學務主任張業崇先生出嚟接信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點知...</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R3uWrDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3uWrDv.jpg&h=dff99bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syJcKqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsyJcKqb.jpg&h=feff7785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張主任黑哂面咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咪好唔想接啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n聽師妹講張主任一接完信就轉身走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦哂班學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽聞東華一早出咗內部信比中學校長<br />\n話總部離啲學校好遠<br />\n要收學生家長信確保安全喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你都知遠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑面接封信就縮返入去！！</span><br />\n收信擺明為秋後算帳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n18中得一間喺港島咋<br />\n咁多學生過海嚟交信<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你黑乜撚嘢面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a3443008b181434b4cd8dc580e1927420faa2c14","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d18fd93044bfaa8c08ed950c88f0cac01fc8ce2","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"429af5ec8a788c5c690dcab5aff41bacabebad67","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"04b8fbf1442575c0f94b42768566da64052e9b4d","tid":1498282,"uid":23829,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"估計封信已經入左垃圾桶"},{"pid":"cffd5d657997d3e3867d3af1edde1691c02f16c0","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"一中 黃笏南"},{"pid":"0bb9e0d2c53ea6bed757c627869f639c258a4a8d","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"二中 李潤田"},{"pid":"506f505e130eff3ac6dd4671e21cbc1ed4adf59e","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"三中 張明添"},{"pid":"6774d7c27e564a763d1d3535ca00cc63163c79e9","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"四中 陳兆民"},{"pid":"785ff71f69589da0c95be8a304b8ac41fc92cc93","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"五中 辛亥年"},{"pid":"69130b2d603b8f1d17f82366dd89cf679c328931","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"六中 伍若瑜"},{"pid":"5b80c51453c7fc013d3a219f9b45c15ac3275efc","tid":1498282,"uid":202269,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"七中 馮黃鳳婷"},{"pid":"a04f054e3551544c72e3580a1394b65ebf255de6","tid":1498282,"uid":264121,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔好捐錢"},{"pid"